            <div type="textpart" xml:id="ThreeChildren"><label>Antiphon of Three Children (ዘ፫ደቂቅ፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Gabriel"><label>Antiphon of the Archangel Gabriel (ዘገብርኤል፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Christmas"><label>Antiphon of Christmas (ዘጌና፡ ክርስቶስ፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Nativity"><label>Antiphon of the Nativity (ዘልደት፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="AfterChristmas"><label>Antiphon of the day after Christmas (ዘሳኒታ፡ ጌና፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="SundayChristmas"><label>Antiphon of the Sunday after Christmas (ዘሰንበተ፡ በዓለ፡ እግዚእነ፡)</label></div>
