            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Matta2"><label>Antiphon of ʾAbbā Maṭṭāʿ or Libānos (ዘአባ፡ መጣዕ፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="EpiphanyEve"><label>Antiphon of Epiphany Eve (ዘመኃትወ፡ ኤጰፋንያ፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Epiphany1"><label>Antiphon of Epiphany (ዘዕለተ፡ ኤጲፋንያ፡ or ዘአስተርእዮ፡)</label></div>
