            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Annunciation"><label>Antiphon of the Annunciation (ዘዜና፡ ገብርኤል፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="PalmSunday"><label>Antiphon of the Palm Sunday (ዘሆሣዕና፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="EasterEve1"><label>Antiphon of Easter Eve, i.e. Good Friday (ዘመኃትወ፡ ፋሲካ፡ መዋሥእት፡ ዘሰርክ፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="EasterEve2"><label>Antiphon of other Easter Eve, i.e. Holy Saturday (ዘዳግም፡ or ዘሰንበተ፡ አይሁድ፡ በመኃትወ፡ ፋሲካ፡ ነግህ፡)</label></div>          
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="EasterSunday"><label>Antiphon of Easter (ዘዕለተ፡ ፋሲካ፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="EasterMonday"><label>Antiphon of Easter Monday (ዘሰኑየ፡ ፋሲካ፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="EasterTuesday"><label>Antiphon of Easter Tuesday (ዘሠሉሰ፡ ፋሲካ፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="EasterWednesday"><label>Antiphon of Easter Wednesday (ዘረቡዐ፡ ፋሲካ፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="EasterThursday"><label>Antiphon of Easter Thursday (ዘኀሙሰ፡ ፋሲካ፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="EasterFriday"><label>Antiphon of Easter Friday (ዘዐርበ፡ ፋሲካ፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="EasterSaturday"><label>Antiphon of Easter Saturday (ዘሰቡዐ፡ ፋሲካ፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="InAlbis"><label>Antiphon of the Dominica In Albis (ዘሰንበተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ or ዘጥልቀተ፡ ፋሲካ፡ or ዘ፰፡ ፋሲካ፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Garments"><label>Antiphon of Garments of the Virgins (ዘአንብሮ፡ አልባስ፡ ዘደናግል፡)</label></div> <!-- ?? -->
