            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Egypt"><label>Antiphon of the Flight to Egypt (ዘበአተ፡ ግብጽ፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Ascension"><label>Antiphon of the Ascension Day (ዘበዓለ፡ ፵ or ዘዕለተ፡ ዕርገት፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Awet"><label>Antiphon of the Nativity of John the Baptist, on the 30 Sane (ዘአዌት፡ ዮሐንስ)</label></div>
