            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Michael2"><label>Antiphon of Michael (ዘሚካኤል፡)</label></div>            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Garima1"><label>Antiphon of ʾAbbā Garimā (ዘአባ፡ ገሪማ፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Garima2"><label>Antiphon of ʾAbbā Garimā (ዘአባ፡ ገሪማ፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Apostles"><label>Antiphon of the Apostles (ዘሐዋርያት፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Qirqos"><label>Antiphon of Cyriacus (ዘቂርቆስ፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Virgins"><label>Antiphon of the Virgins (ዘደናግል፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Firstborn"><label>Antiphon of the Firstborn (ዘማኅበረ፡ በኵር፡)</label>
