            </div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="DabraTabor"><label>Antiphon of Mount Tabor, i.e. the Transfiguration of Jesus Christ (ዘደብረ፡ ታቦር፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Mary"><label>Antiphon of Our Lady Mary (ዘእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Abraham"><label>Antiphon of Abraham (ዘአብርሃም፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Melchizedek"><label>Antiphon of Melchizedek (ዘመልከ፡ ጼዴቅ፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Beheading"><label>Antiphon of Beheading (ዘምትረተ፡ ርእሱ፡ ለዮሐንስ፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Libanos"><label>Antiphon of ʾAbbā Libānos</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Pilgrims"><label>Antiphon of Pilgrims (ዘፈላስያን፡)</label></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Sunday"><label>Antiphon of Sunday  (ዘሰንበተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡)</label></div>
